<LanguageData>
	
	<!-- EN: ear rot -->
	<Mousekin_EarRot.label>耳腐病</Mousekin_EarRot.label>
	
	<!-- EN: A fungal infection unique to Mousekins, caused by not cleaning one's ears regularly and properly. If left untreated, the disease gradually necrotizes the ear's tissues and results in permanent hearing loss.\n\nThis infection can be slowly treated by repeated tending with medicine, or quickly cured with an Elixir of Harmony. -->
	<Mousekin_EarRot.description>白鼠族特有的真菌感染，源于未定期妥善清洁耳部。若未及时治疗，此病症将逐渐导致耳部组织坏死，造成永久性听力损失。\n\n此感染可透过反覆用药缓慢治疗，或使用白鼠族和谐灵丹快速治愈。</Mousekin_EarRot.description>
	
	<!-- EN: minor -->
	<Mousekin_EarRot.stages.0.label>轻度</Mousekin_EarRot.stages.0.label>
	
	<!-- EN: major -->
	<Mousekin_EarRot.stages.1.label>中度</Mousekin_EarRot.stages.1.label>
	
	<!-- EN: serious -->
	<Mousekin_EarRot.stages.2.label>重度</Mousekin_EarRot.stages.2.label>
	
	<!-- EN: extreme -->
	<Mousekin_EarRot.stages.3.label>极重度</Mousekin_EarRot.stages.3.label>
	
	<!-- EN: {PAWN_labelShort}'s {1} was destroyed by ear rot. -->
	<Mousekin_EarRot.comps.HediffComp_DestroyOrgan.messageText>{PAWN_labelShort}的{1}因耳腐病而被摧毁。</Mousekin_EarRot.comps.HediffComp_DestroyOrgan.messageText>
	
</LanguageData>